arts.ttl: Schalke go top with a comfortable win in Hannover
arts.sum: Two African strikers helped Schalke to climb to the top of 2. Bundesliga.

arts.ttl: 2. Bundesliga Friday Konferenz: Hannover and Schalke target top spot, Anfang debut in Düsseldorf
arts.sum: On Friday, either Schalke or Hannover could momentarily go top of the 2. Bundesliga, and there will be a coaching debut in Düsseldorf for Markus Anfang.
